data.description: We are thrilled to introduce you to your new haven at Valencia del Sol! Step into the warmth of this exceptional 55+ community, designed for those who truly savor life's pleasures. The TRIBECA FLOORPLAN, featuring 3 bedrooms, a den, and 2 1/2 baths, offers versatile space to tailor your home to your unique desires and requirements. With a myriad of activities and amenities at your disposal, you'll find endless opportunities to relish every moment.    Picture starting your day with an invigorating dip in the resort-style pool, followed by a leisurely stroll through the neighborhood. Later, you can engage in a fun game of pickleball or tennis with newfound friends or indulge your furry companion at the dog park. Thanks to golf cart accessibility throughout the community, you can effortlessly visit the clubhouse for a delectable meal at the restaurant or catch a movie in the theater. When it's time to unwind, retreat to your luxurious abode and take in the tranquil vista of the lake from your enclosed and temperature-controlled patio.    Speaking of your new home, it is an absolute gem. The split-plan layout ensures privacy, with the master bedroom thoughtfully separated from the other two bedrooms. The open floor plan facilitates seamless entertaining, and the kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring top-tier quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. The coffered ceilings in the foyer add an extra touch of sophistication, while the sliding glass doors leading to the patio create an indoor/outdoor living space ideally suited for Florida's temperate climate. Furthermore, thoughtful upgrades like the fully enclosed patio and generous closet space in the master bedroom will make you feel like royalty in your new residence.    Let's not overlook the community itself. The HOA fee covers lawn and tree maintenance, cable services, and a security system, ensuring you can savor all the amenities without added worries. Speaking of amenities, the clubhouse is truly remarkable. From the theater and fitness center to the activity and game rooms, there's always an array of enjoyable pursuits. The pool area is a paradise within this paradise, complete with furnished cabanas and a cozy fireplace seating area. With gated and manned security, you'll experience a profound sense of safety and serenity in your new home.    At Valencia del Sol, you'll be embraced by a lively and engaged community that treasures the good life. Don't let this exclusive opportunity pass you by – join us at Valencia del Sol and begin living your best life.
